{"tid":2347843,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–針對新陳代謝來醫治癌症(一)","createTime":"2020-12-31T10:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T13:36:08.000Z","uid":38861,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"85324958a3d992610a0469ec23ecc94539029e04","tid":2347843,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"透過進食，我們能夠從食物中獲取身體所需的能量。這過程亦稱之為新陳代謝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmJjBRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmJjBRk.jpg&h=f9419265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無數證據顯示，癌細胞的新陳代謝與正常的細胞有著顯著的分別。<br />\n正因如此，有不少科學家抱有一個信念，希望透過針對癌細胞的新陳代謝來抑止癌細胞的生長，甚至是達消滅癌細胞之效。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）半胱胺酸 (Cysteine)是氨基酸的一種，亦即是組成蛋白質的基本單元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3k9Y4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3k9Y4H.jpg&h=21308ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們可以透過直接進食來攝取Cysteine，又或者依靠肝臟將特定兩隻氨基酸(Methionine及Serine)轉化成為Cysteine供我們所用。<br />\n<br />\n有科學家嘗試從飼養癌細胞的營養液中剔除Cysteine，發覺部份癌細胞的生長速度有所減慢，而有部份的癌細胞則趨向死亡(Ref1)。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）從營養液剔除Cysteine後，身體攝取Cysteine的辦法便只剩下依靠肝臟將同為氨基酸的Methionine及Serine轉化成為Cysteine。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nF2Aabq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnF2Aabq.jpg&h=cc0e19d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而各種剔除Cysteine便會死亡的癌細胞的共通點，就是缺乏一隻名為5-methylthioadenosine phosphorylase(MTAP)的蛋白酶。<br />\n<br />\n失去MTAP後，細胞會傾向將Methionine轉化成為一系列名為Polyamine的物質，導致身體失去製作Cysteine的手段。<br />\n<br />\n更甚的是，產生Polyamine的過程中將會產生游離基，而制衝游離基的Glutathione卻則依靠Cysteine作為原材料。<br />\n<br />\n因此，缺乏MTAP的癌細胞若然沒有外來Cysteine供應的話，便會因游離基數量過多而導致死亡。<br />\n<br />\n環觀各種癌細胞，膠質母細胞瘤（Glioblastoma)有較大的機會因基因變異而失去MTAP基因。<br />\n<br />\n根據上述研究結果，若癌症病人的癌細胞證實缺乏MTAP基因的話，在餐單中剔除進食Cysteine氨基酸或許是一個副作用相對上為微的理性選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。</span><br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=9b432d1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=df476c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=3d0c224d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s42255-020-0253-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs42255-020-0253-2&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=63805637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s42255-020-0253-2</a>"},{"pid":"a70da2487fccadcf34cc9afaee822984456108d9","tid":2347843,"uid":5087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而制衝游離基的Glutathione卻則依靠Cysteine作為原材料。</blockqu